# Node.js Contact Form Backend

This is a simple Node.js + Express backend that handles a contact form and sends emails using Nodemailer and Gmail SMTP.

## 🚀 Features

- 📩 Contact form using plain HTML
- 📨 Sends submitted data to your Gmail
- 🌐 Built with Express and Nodemailer
- 🔐 Uses `.env` for email credentials

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Node.js
- Express
- Nodemailer
- Gmail SMTP
- dotenv

## 📁 Project Structure

project/
│
├── app.js # Main backend file
├── .env # Email credentials (excluded from GitHub)
├── .gitignore
└── README.md


1. **Clone the repo**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/danish-sai/contact-form-backend
   cd contact-form-backend
Install dependencies

npm install
Create a .env file

EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your-16-digit-app-password
Run the app

node app.js

use the postman to add the data 


http://localhost:3000
